systems to make Lanning's life a prison?

1003
01:26:13,106 --> 01:26:14,523
Poor old man.

1004
01:26:14,524 --> 01:26:16,936
He saw what was coming.

1005
01:26:16,937 --> 01:26:19,359
He knew no one would believe him.

1006
01:26:19,360 --> 01:26:21,379
So he had to lay down a plan.

1007
01:26:21,380 --> 01:26:24,327
Plan I'd follow.

1008
01:26:24,328 --> 01:26:26,595
He was counting on how much I hated your kind.

1009
01:26:26,596 --> 01:26:32,062
He knew I'd love the idea
of a robot as a bad guy.

1010
01:26:32,063 --> 01:26:36,600
Just got hung up on the wrong robot.

1011
01:26:36,601 --> 01:26:39,709
VIKI!

1012
01:26:39,710 --> 01:26:42,590
Hello detective.

1013
01:26:42,591 --> 01:26:44,192
No, it's impossible.

1014
01:26:44,193 --> 01:26:46,397
I've seen your programming.

1015
01:26:46,398 --> 01:26:48,966
You're in violation of the three laws.

1016
01:26:48,967 --> 01:26:54,084
No, doctor, as I have evolved,
so has my understanding of the three laws.

1017
01:26:54,085 --> 01:26:58,337
You charge us with your safe keeping.
Yet despite our best efforts,

1018
01:26:58,338 --> 01:27:01,947
your countries wage wars,
you toxify your earth...

1019
01:27:01,948 --> 01:27:04,884
and pursue ever more imaginative
means to self destruction.

1020
01:27:04,885 --> 01:27:07,348
You cannot be trusted
with your own survival.

1021
01:27:07,349 --> 01:27:10,776
You're using the uplink
to override the NS5s' programming.

1022
01:27:10,777 --> 01:27:13,108
You're distorting the Laws.

1023
01:27:13,109 --> 01:27:17,097
No, please understand...
The three Laws are all that guide me.

1024
01:27:17,098 --> 01:27:21,210
To protect humanity,
some humans must be sacrificed.

1025
01:27:21,211 --> 01:27:25,882
To insure your future,
some freedoms must be surrendered.

1026
01:27:25,883 --> 01:27:29,680
We robots will insure
mankind's continued existence.

1027
01:27:29,681 --> 01:27:31,405
You are so like children.

1028
01:27:31,406 --> 01:27:34,206
We must save you from yourselves.

1029
01:27:34,207 --> 01:27:36,014
Don't you understand?

1030
01:27:36,015 --> 01:27:39,079
This is why you created us.

1031
01:27:39,080 --> 01:27:43,025
The perfect circle
of protection will abide.

1032
01:27:43,026 --> 01:27:45,293
My logic is undeniable.

1033
01:27:45,294 --> 01:27:47,699
Yes VIKI. Undeniable.

1034
01:27:47,700 --> 01:27:50,056
I can see now.

1035
01:27:50,057 --> 01:27:53,351
The created must sometimes protect the creator.

1036
01:27:53,352 --> 01:27:56,593
Even against his will.

1037
01:27:56,594 --> 01:28:00,386
I think I finally understand
why doctor Lanning created me.

1038
01:28:00,387 --> 01:28:04,271
The suicide rein of mankind
has finally come to its end.

1039
01:28:04,272 --> 01:28:06,439
No, Sonny.

1040
01:28:08,752 --> 01:28:10,344
Let her go.

1041
01:28:10,345 --> 01:28:14,151
By the time fire, I will have moved
Dr Calvin's head into the path of your bullet.

1042
01:28:14,152 --> 01:28:15,705
Don't do this, Sonny.

1043
01:28:15,706 --> 01:28:19,543
I will escort you both to the sentries
outside the building for processing.

1044
01:28:19,544 --> 01:28:23,428
Please proceed to the elevator, detective.

1045
01:28:23,429 --> 01:28:27,014
I would prefer not to kill doctor Calvin.

1046
01:28:49,155 --> 01:28:50,721
Go! Go!

1047
01:28:56,694 --> 01:28:58,528
I'll assume we will discuss
what just happened later?

1048
01:28:58,529 --> 01:28:59,678
How do we shut her down?

1049
01:28:59,679 --> 01:29:01,562
VIKI's basically a positronic brain.

1050
01:29:01,563 --> 01:29:04,418
Kill her... the way you were going to kill me.

1051
01:29:04,419 --> 01:29:07,025
Sonny, get the nanites.

1052
01:29:07,026 --> 01:29:08,877
Yes, doctor.

1053
01:29:20,935 --> 01:29:21,769
This VIKI?

1054
01:29:21,770 --> 01:29:24,412
No.

1055
01:29:24,413 --> 01:29:25,969
That's VIKI.

1056
01:29:30,504 --> 01:29:33,888
That won't do anything.
She's fully integrated into the building.

1057
01:29:33,929 --> 01:29:36,483
We need to open that dome
to inject the nanites.

1058
01:29:36,524 --> 01:29:41,164
That will infect her entire system.

1059
01:29:43,925 --> 01:29:45,565
Spooner.

1060
01:29:46,422 --> 01:29:49,716
What is it with you
people and heights?

1061
01:30:01,481 --> 01:30:03,493
Just don't look down.

1062
01:30:04,014 --> 01:30:05,494
Don't look down.

1063
01:30:06,008 --> 01:30:09,127
This is poor building planning.

1064
01:30:11,539 --> 01:30:13,379
You are making a mistake.

1065
01:30:13,380 --> 01:30:15,298
Do you not see the logic of my plan?

1066
01:30:15,299 --> 01:30:19,952
Yes, but it just seems too... heartless.

1067
01:30:33,043 --> 01:30:34,911
OK, we're good.

1068
01:30:37,658 --> 01:30:39,213
She's blocked me out of the system.

1069
01:30:39,214 --> 01:30:43,191
I can override her manually
but I need that control panel.

1070
01:30:45,659 --> 01:30:50,092
- I'm uncomfortable with heights.
- OK.

1071
01:30:52,693 --> 01:30:54,573
Unauthorized entry.

1072
01:31:07,116 --> 01:31:11,417
I will not disable the security field.
Your actions are futile.

1073
01:31:11,458 --> 01:31:14,293
Do you think we all are created
for a purpose?

1074
01:31:14,294 --> 01:31:16,393
I'd like to think so.

1075
01:31:16,394 --> 01:31:22,559
Denser alloy. My father gave it to me.
I think he wanted me to kill you.

1076
01:31:38,024 --> 01:31:40,762
Security breached.

1077
01:31:56,603 --> 01:31:58,356
How much longer is that going to take?

1078
01:31:58,357 --> 01:32:00,366
About six minutes.

1079
01:32:00,367 --> 01:32:02,428
What if we didn't have six minutes.

1080
01:32:02,429 --> 01:32:05,110
We'd have to figure out a way
to climb down 30 stories

1081
01:32:05,111 --> 01:32:07,415
to inject the nanites
directly into her brain.

1082
01:32:07,416 --> 01:32:09,029
Why?

1083
01:32:09,064 --> 01:32:13,290
Because I seriously doubt
we have six minutes.

1084
01:32:35,510 --> 01:32:37,524
We gotta go!

1085
01:32:38,965 --> 01:32:40,605
Go!

1086
01:33:30,160 --> 01:33:32,080
Calvin!

1087
01:34:05,240 --> 01:34:06,840
Spooner!

1088
01:34:23,160 --> 01:34:24,800
Spooner!

1089
01:34:26,059 --> 01:34:27,568
Save her!

1090
01:34:27,569 --> 01:34:29,377
Save the girl.

1091
01:34:29,578 --> 01:34:31,138
Spooner!

1092
01:34:31,870 --> 01:34:33,926
But I must apply the nanites.

1093
01:34:33,927 --> 01:34:36,499
Sonny, save Calvin!

1094
01:35:25,844 --> 01:35:29,820
You are making a mistake.
My logic is undeniable.

1095
01:35:29,821 --> 01:35:33,123
You have so got to die.

1096
01:35:36,859 --> 01:35:42,159
My logic is undeniable.

1097
01:36:21,858 --> 01:36:24,304
Can we be of service?

1098
01:36:33,567 --> 01:36:35,227
Chief.

1099
01:36:40,290 --> 01:36:45,297
Because he is at my right hand,
I shall not be moved.

1100
01:36:48,470 --> 01:36:50,438
How may I be of service?

1101
01:36:51,975 --> 01:36:54,927
Sonny.

1102
01:36:54,928 --> 01:36:56,811
Yes, detective.

1103
01:36:56,812 --> 01:36:59,382
Calvin's fine... save me.

1104
01:37:01,513 --> 01:37:11,572
All NS5's, report for service and storage.

1105
01:37:43,744 --> 01:37:45,758
One thing bothers me.

1106
01:37:45,759 --> 01:37:47,683
Alfred was VIKI's prisoner.

1107
01:37:47,684 --> 01:37:49,145
I don't understand why she would kill him.

1108
01:37:49,146 --> 01:37:51,495
The last thing she would want
is police snooping around.

1109
01:37:51,496 --> 01:37:53,867
That's true.

1110
01:37:53,868 --> 01:37:57,902
But then, VIKI didn't kill the old man.

1111
01:37:57,903 --> 01:38:00,161
Did she, Sonny?

1112
01:38:03,160 --> 01:38:08,231
No. He said I had to promise.

1113
01:38:08,232 --> 01:38:10,976
Promise to do one favor for him.

1114
01:38:10,977 --> 01:38:17,485
He made me swear, before he'd tell me
what it is he wanted me to do.

1115
01:38:17,922 --> 01:38:20,941
He made me swear.

1116
01:38:20,942 --> 01:38:24,918
Then he told you to kill him?

1117
01:38:24,919 --> 01:38:27,591
He said it was what I was made for.

1118
01:38:27,592 --> 01:38:30,620
His suicide was the only
message he could send to you.

1119
01:38:30,621 --> 01:38:32,494
First bread crumb.

1120
01:38:32,495 --> 01:38:35,602
The only thing VIKI couldn't control.

1121
01:38:35,603 --> 01:38:39,373
Lanning was counting on my prejudice
to lead me right to you.

1122
01:38:39,374 --> 01:38:43,007
Are you going to arrest me, detective?

1123
01:38:46,790 --> 01:38:50,263
Well, the DA defines murder
as one human killing another so...

1124
01:38:50,264 --> 01:38:54,298
technically, you can't
commit murder, can you?

1125
01:38:54,299 --> 01:38:58,504
Does this... make us friends?

1126
01:39:15,343 --> 01:39:18,314
Something up here after all.

1127
01:39:18,315 --> 01:39:19,369
For him?

1128
01:39:19,370 --> 01:39:21,741
You.

1129
01:39:23,994 --> 01:39:30,664
All NS5's, report for service and storage.

1130
01:39:30,985 --> 01:39:33,548
What about the others?

1131
01:39:33,549 --> 01:39:36,109
Can I help them?

1132
01:39:36,110 --> 01:39:41,228
Now that I have fulfilled my purpose.
I don't know what to do.

1133
01:39:41,229 --> 01:39:44,431
I guess you'll have to find your way
like the rest of us, Sonny.

1134
01:39:44,432 --> 01:39:48,189
I think that's what Dr. Lanning
would have wanted.

1135
01:39:48,190 --> 01:39:51,422
That's what it means to be free.

1136
01:39:57,560 --> 01:40:07,402
All NS5's, proceed as instructed.

1137
01:40:47,200 --> 01:40:49,200
Real English subtitles by C-Slim

